https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500null Andala Ramudu is a Telugu film released on August 11, 2006 starring Sunil and Aarti Agarwal. This film was directed by P Lakshmi Narayana and produced by NV Prasad and Paras Jain. This movie is the remake of Tamil film Sundara Purushan starring Livingston and Rambha. Andala Ramudu
